This is the README file for the `ginnungagap' distribution.
Ginnungagap is a tool to generate initial conditions.

  Copyright (C) 2010, 2011, 2012, Steffen Knollmann, 
                2013, 2014, Sergey Pilipenko

  Copying and distribution of this file, with or without modification,
  are permitted in any medium without royalty provided the copyright
  notice and this notice are preserved.

See the file ./BUILD for quick building instructions, however, it is
recommended to built the code documentation for a detailed description
of the code.

See the file ./NEWS for an overview of the changes to the code between
the different releases and hence a description of the latest changes.

Home page:  http://ginnungagapgroup.github.io/ginnungagap/
Contact:    spilipenko@asc.rssi.ru

Ginnungagap is free software.  See the file COPYING for copying
conditions.
